#: ../../docs/classes/class_basis.rst:17
msgid ""
"3×3 matrix used for 3D rotation and scale. Contains 3 vector fields X, Y "
"and Z as its columns, which can be interpreted as the local basis vectors"
" of a transformation. Can also be accessed as array of 3D vectors. These "
"vectors are orthogonal to each other, but are not necessarily normalized "
"(due to scaling). Almost always used as an orthogonal basis for a "
":ref:`Transform <class_Transform>`."
msgstr ""
"3×3矩阵，用于3D旋转和缩放。包含3个向量字段X、Y和Z作为其列，这些字段可以解释为变换的局部基础向量。也可以作为3D向量数组访问。这些向量彼此正交，但不一定要归一化（由于缩放）。对于一个"
" :ref:`Transform <class_Transform>`，几乎总是用作一个正交基础。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_basis.rst:19
msgid ""
"For such use, it is composed of a scaling and a rotation matrix, in that "
"order (M = R.S)."
msgstr "对于这种用途，它由一个缩放和一个旋转矩阵，按该顺序（``M = R.S``）组成。"

